# 🦅 Haribon Real Estate - User Manual
**Mobile-First Property Platform | User Experience & Technical Documentation**

Haribon is a premium real estate e-commerce system built to provide a seamless property browsing and acquisition experience. This manual walks through the platform's core functionalities, optimized for both desktop and high-performance mobile viewing.

---

## 🏠 1. The Landing Experience
The Haribon homepage is designed to establish brand trust and provide immediate access to property categories.

![Hero Sections](homepage1.png)
![Secondary Landing](homepage2.png)

* **Brand Identity:** High-contrast dark mode aesthetic for a luxury real estate feel.
* **Core Qualities:** The **qualities.png** section highlights the platform's unique selling points (Security, Value, Luxury).
* **Featured Residences:** A direct link to top-tier listings via the **residences.png** portal.

---

## 🔑 2. Secure Onboarding & Authentication
Haribon utilizes a specialized mobile-centric authentication layout to ensure ease of use on touch devices.

![Login & Signup](login.png)
![Signup Process](signup.png)

* **Mobile-Optimized UI:** Vertical form layouts designed specifically for single-hand thumb navigation.
* **Subscription Management:** Users can manage recurring alerts and premium memberships via **subscription.png**.

---

## 🔍 3. Property Search & Discovery
The heart of Haribon is its efficient search and filtering engine, allowing users to find their dream home in seconds.

### Dynamic Filtering & Sorting
![Sorting Logic](sorting.png)

* **Property Categories:** Filter by Apartment, Commercial, Condominium, Foreclosure, or House.
* **Advanced Sorting:** Organize listings by price, date added, or popularity via **sorting.png**.

### The Listing Gallery
![Property List](property-list.png)

* **Grid View:** High-density property cards showing price and location at a glance.
* **Favorites System:** Users can save properties for later review using the **favorite-tab.png** feature.

---

## 📄 4. Property Deep-Dive
Detailed property pages provide all the technical data needed for a buyer to make an informed decision.

![Property Details 1](property-page1.png)
![Property Details 2](property-page2.png)

* **Visual Galleries:** High-resolution image sliders for interior and exterior views.
* **Specifications:** Detailed breakdown of floor area, amenities, and neighborhood data.

