## 📞 5. Lead Generation & Contact
Haribon bridges the gap between buyers and estate agents with integrated communication tools.

![Contact Interface](contacts.png)

* **Direct Inquiries:** A dedicated **contacts.png** portal for scheduling property viewings.
* **Agent Connectivity:** One-tap calling and emailing features optimized for mobile users.

